The menu includes a sandwich which costs $15%2C and a soup which costs $10%2C as well pizza and other things.

There is a special today. If you order both the sandwich and soup%2C you get a discount. Instead of paying 25 Dollars%2C you pay only 15 Dollars.

You ask Alex%2C "What did you order?"

She responds%2C "I ordered the sandwich."

How likely is it%2C in your opinion%2C that she also ordered soup?
